node.text: @womenofimpact ROUND 3!!! (link to full video in my bio) !!!! This is the third time my sweet friend @lisabilyeu and I have sat down to avaaa chat. And I am always just so shocked after because we get into such a beautiful flow we have healthy debate we discuss things and unpack them deeply. I love her so much and I really hope this conversation is useful in some way. It's almost like a therapy session for me, say things I didn't intend to felt things I didn't know I needed to.  It was CLEANSING 😂😂😅😅

node.text: YOU GOT THIS. NEW WEEK NEW ENERGY. LETS GOOOOO!! but also if you’re having a meltdown and have them regularly like me..don’t worry 🌸 little tiny steps.. that’s all you need xxx

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Radhi Devlukia-Shetty on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'We have to let go in order to create space to recieve more, to recieve better. There are always things we need to shed and let go of, some old we've kept in the dark corners of our mind and some new that are at the top of the pile! Letting go has to be a part of the natural cycle of life, we are so used to holding on, hording and wanting to preserve everything that we forget to let go of the things that no longer need to be part of us. Radhi'.

node.text: Take a moment to think, what do I need to let go of today!? Lemme tell you everyday I do that i come up with a wholleeeeee lot 💛 we need to stop seeing letting go as a LOSS. don't be afraid to let go and embrace what is..it's in the past for good reason it had its time now it's ti@e to Acknowledge it Appreciate it then lovingly let go 💛 #quotes #quoteoftheday

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Radhi Devlukia-Shetty on July 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Truth: You won't always be liked by everyone. Your energies just may not match. Sometimes there's no specific reason, its just a feeling, a discomfort, a disconnect. So don't spend your life trying to be the person they will like, spend it trying to be the person you like, because when you like you, whether others do or don't won't bother you as much! Radhi'.

node.text: It is what it is!!! Focus on being the best you not the you you think they want you to be! 💛🌸 #quotes #quoteoftheday

node.text: @womenofimpact ROUND 3!!! (link to full video in my bio) !!!! This is the third time my sweet friend @lisabilyeu and I have sat down to avaaa chat. And I am always just so shocked after because we get into such a beautiful flow we have healthy debate we discuss things and unpack them deeply. I love her so much and I really hope this conversation is useful in some way. It's almost like a therapy session for me, say things I didn't intend to felt things I didn't know I needed to.  It was CLEANSING 😂😂😅😅

node.text:
5 THINGS TO TRY TO HELP YOU 💩

1. SPICE UP YOUR LIFE - cumin, coriander and fennel aid digestion and relax stomach muscles. Saute and add them into your curries or roast the seeds and grind all 3 spices into powder and sprinkle onto anything! 

2. KEEP IT MOVING🏃🏾‍♀️
Aerobic exercise increases blood flow to digestive organs and increases strength h of intestinal muscles 

3. CHEW PROPERLY - the more you chew the easier it is to digest the easier it is to 💩

4. STOMACH MASSAGE
- 5-10 mins relaxes muscles and moves it along! 

 5 TRIPHALA POWDER 
- a natural laxitive. Take 1/2 tsp in 1/2 cup warm water before bed. 

Happy 💩ing
